trans-unit.source: Specifies whether the current value of **DefineConstants** is kept, which affects target assembly generation; if this parameter is changed, the public API in the target assembly may be changed and the compilation of [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_titlexaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-titlexaml-md.md)] files that reference local types may be affected.
